OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a generally cloudy
OL,6,Fday, with areas of haar especially
OL,7,Fnear northern and eastern coasts and
OL,8,Fhigh ground. A little brightness west
OL,9,Fof hills, before outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fdevelop during the afternoon. Light
OL,11,Fwinds, humid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain, and fairly widespread haar,
OL,15,Fthough Orkney should become dry with
OL,16,Fthe haar clearing later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
