OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FShetland damp with some
OL,6,Fhaar in the morning then brightening
OL,7,Fup in the afternoon with sunny
OL,8,Fintervals. Orkney dry for much of day,
OL,9,Fsome sunny intervals, then showers
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FThursday and early Friday mostly
OL,14,Fcloudy with some showery rain, then
OL,15,Flater Friday and Saturday mainly dry
OL,16,Fand bright with some sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
